<el-tooltip
  effect="dark"
  :content="tooltipContent"
  placement="bottom">
  <el-button
    class="d2-ml-0 d2-mr btn-text can-hover"
    type="text"
    @click="handleClick">
    <el-badge
      v-if="logLength > 0"
      :max="99"
      :value="logLengthError"
      :is-dot="logLengthError === 0">
      <d2-icon
        :name="logLengthError === 0 ? 'dot-circle-o' : 'bug'"
        style="font-size: 20px"/>
    </el-badge>
    <d2-icon
      v-else
      name="dot-circle-o"
      style="font-size: 20px"/>
  </el-button>
</el-tooltip>
